Encrypted Image with text: Made by Blauharley

  
  
    var img = new Image();

    img.onload = function(){

      var crypto = new LoremImageCryptonator();
      crypto.setImage(img);
      crypto.getCryptoImage('Made by Blauharley',function(cimg){
         document.body.appendChild(cimg);
      });
      
    };

    img.src='img/desert.jpg';

Extracted text out of Encrypted Image 

  
    var cimg = document.getElementById('encryptedImg');
	
    var crypto = new LoremImageCryptonator();
    var extractedtext = crypto.getTextFromCryptoImage(cimg);
